1.text: The first kiss is more likely to happen when nobody else is around.

2.text: Eye contact shows attraction and confidence.

3.text: Smiling shows that special someone that you’re feeling them.

4.text: A gentle touch is another way to show attraction to someone.

5.text: This gets your lips nice and close for a kiss.

6.text: A not-so-subtle hint might be all it takes to get that first kiss.

7.text: An intimate dance is the perfect moment for a first kiss.

8.text: A little pampering makes your lips look extra kissable.

9.text: A cheek kiss can lead to a kiss on the lips.

10.text: Your crush might be holding back because they aren’t sure if you want to kiss.
